Title: [5G18A] 16 unit synchronisation failed [ASIK/ABIL]
Description:
[1. Test scenario]
- updated onto soft 5GBTS_18A_4.32111.83
- tweaked to get x2 communication and commisioned 

[2. Fault description]
a minut after radio is green unit synchro error occurs.
After that there is automatic site reboot.
To get snapshot it was necessary to disable automatic reboots.

[3. Tester analysis]
NA

[4. Fault repeatibility]
every time.

[5. Test scenario history of execution]


[6. Test line reference / info]
test line Wroclaw c1800-t02
NCIR17A patch 19, AMIA A203, ASIK X22, ABIL X13, FYGB, AEUA x31, Dell optical switch. 


[7. Log file contents]
NCIR "collect all" logs

[8. Test case ID]

[9. Customer impact analysis]

Title: 5GC000380-381-382-NiDD parameter Missing-DetectedspeedAndDuplex in ETHLK
Description:
1.4.5 Licensing
The usage of the SFP+ Slot in ASIK is licensed. The feature activation is tracked by checking DetectedspeedAndDuplex parameter in ETHLK. Whenever the value indicates "10GBIT_FULL" for this interface and the interface is activated, then the 10G is assumed to be used and shall be charged (the same principle should apply for 25GE in furture).

Actual : NIDD DetectedspeedAndDuplex is missing

Expected : DetectedspeedAndDuplex availability.
